data.description:
Welcome to your new dream home in Delray Beach! This spectacular four bedroom, three bathroom home sits on a double lot of 24,871 sq ft, providing you with ample space to make your dreams a reality. Upon entering the home, you will be greeted by the grand double door entry into the foyer, featuring storage spaces for your guests' coats. The open kitchen area is perfect for entertaining, with plenty of room to cook and serve your favorite meals. The living room, dining area, and family room are also open, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. The family room features French doors that lead into the enclosed Florida room, providing additional space for relaxation or entertainment. The large master bedroom is a true oasis, featuring a huge walk-in closet and a spacious bathroom

The other three bedrooms are also generously sized, and the second bathroom features dual sinks and a linen closet.

The backyard is an outdoor lover's paradise, with plenty of room for a pool, gazebo, fire pit, and even a shed for additional storage. The absence of an HOA allows you to let your imagination run wild with the amount of space available. You can even split the lot and build two new homes!

With 2,850 living square feet and a total of 3,856 total square feet, this property is just waiting for your personal touches and upgrades to call it home. Imagine creating your own private sanctuary in one of the most desirable locations in Delray Beach.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in this sought-after community. This home truly has it all  space, location, and endless possibilities. Come see it for yourself today and start living the Florida lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
